              <p><span class="tui-event">tool-call</span> rg --files src/domains/payments</p>
              <p><span class="tui-event">tool-call</span> read contracts and QA cases</p>
              <p><span class="tui-event">file-change</span> wrote specs/014/spec.md</p>
              <p class="tui-selection"><span class="tui-event">activity</span> Defining bounded task ownership</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="demo-step">
      <div class="step-copy">
        <span class="step-index">04 / APPROVE</span>
        <h3>Review the story before agents act.</h3>
        <p>
          Read the generated Markdown, adjust research and architect settings,
          and approve only when the story, acceptance criteria, and delivery
          detail are right.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="tui-window" aria-label="Conduit Markdown story preview">
        <div class="tui-grid tui-grid-preview">
          <div class="tui-pane tui-sidebar">
            <div class="tui-brand" aria-hidden="true"><span>●──┬─●</span><b>conduit</b></div>
            <p class="tui-label">Refinement fields</p>
            <p class="tui-selection">▸ Problem / user story * · 147</p>
            <p class="tui-muted">&nbsp; User or audience * · 10</p>
            <p class="tui-muted">&nbsp; Desired outcome and acceptance criteria * · 420</p>
            <p class="tui-muted">&nbsp; QA test cases and regressions * · 640</p>
